Package musichub.business

Class LivreAudio

  • java.lang.Object
    • musichub.business.Element
      • musichub.business.LivreAudio
  • public class LivreAudio
extends Element
    LivreAudio is an audio book object in the librairy.

    An audio book can be added and removed from the librairy or a Playlist object.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Sylvain BUI, Maxence LECLERC, Nour-El-Houda LOUATY, Sarra MADAD
    See Also:
    Element, ElementList, Playlist
